spec_data.Name: php-theseer-autoload
spec_data.Description:
The PHP AutoloadBuilder CLI tool phpab is a command line application
to automate the process of generating an autoload require file with
the option of creating static require lists as well as phar archives.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 08 Aug 2017 10:55:24 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A tool and library to generate autoload code
